  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Demonstration blocks Kuri Road after police officer assaults cleric at Vavunia filling station",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Vavuniya, people blocked the road and protested that the police had attacked a cleric at a petrol filling station.",
        "It is reported that a cleric was assaulted by a police officer while people were standing in a long line to get fuel at a fuel station located in the fourth block of Vavuniya Nelukulam.",
        "Following this, the people standing there blocked the Vavuniya Mannar main road and protested and demanded that the police officer should apologize to the priest who was attacked.",
        "Due to this, there was a tense situation and the traffic on Vavunia and Mannar main road was stopped for a long time. Following this, the police officer who visited the spot apologized to the stricken cleric and the demonstration was abandoned."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
